“Commissioner”  means  the  Commissioner  of  Sports  appointed 
under  section  10  and  includes  a  Regional,  Deputy  or  Assistant 
Commissioner of Sports;

“company” has the same meaning as is assigned to that expression 
in  the  Companies  Act  2016  [Act  777]  and  includes  a  “corporation” 
as defined in that Act;

“National  Sports  Council”  means  the  National  Sports  Council  of 
Malaysia established under the National Sports Council of Malaysia 
Act 1971 [Act 29];

(a)  a member of any subcommittee or other body established 
or formed by the governing body of a sports body, or by 
the governing body of a branch of such sports body;

(b)  such sports body shall not receive or continue to receive 
funding  from  the  Government,  the  National  Sports 
Council or any statutory body;

(a)  the  procedure  for  the  application  for  registration  and 
registration  of  sports  bodies  and  the  fees  to  be  charged 
for such registration;

(a)  the  forms  to  be  used  and  the  conditions  to  be  complied 
with  in  applying  to  be  registered  or  licensed  under  this 
Act;
